; User-facing MTProto launcher.
;
; Run from the package drawer:
;   Execute TelegramAmiga
;
; Or attach an IconX project icon named TelegramAmiga.info and double-click it
; from Workbench/Ambient/Wanderer.

FailAt 21
Stack 65536

Execute RunMTProtoStart

IF WARN
    Echo ""
    Echo "TelegramAmiga ended with an error. Read the message above."
    Echo "This window will stay open for 120 seconds."
    Wait 120
ENDIF
